Interface ElementParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CellParser, LabelParser, RowParser, TableParser, TextButtonParser, TextFieldParser

    public interface ElementParser
    The abstract class for element-wise parsers. The implementations of this class have to provide a way to load / save an actor to a XML file.
